sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor A as Staff User
  participant Auth as Auth Middleware
  participant R as Agent Route
  participant C as Ticket Controller
  participant S as Ticket Service
  participant Repo as Ticket Repo
  participant DB as Prisma/PostgreSQL

  A->>Auth: GET /api/agents/me/stats?organizationId=...
  Auth-->>R: req.user
  R->>C: getMyAgentStats(request)
  C->>S: getMyAgentStatsService(query, userId)

  S->>S: getMyAgentTicketsService(query, userId)

  S->>Repo: getTicketMembershipsByUserId(userId)
  Repo->>DB: Membership.findMany(userId)
  DB-->>Repo: memberships
  Repo-->>S: memberships

  alt No staff membership in scope
    S-->>C: throw 403
    C-->>A: 403 response
  else Allowed
    S->>Repo: getAgentTickets(filters)
    Repo->>DB: Ticket.findMany(assignedToId=userId)
    DB-->>Repo: assigned tickets
    Repo-->>S: tickets

    S->>S: aggregate by status and priority
    S-->>C: stats summary
    C-->>A: 200 OK
  end
